    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>A good improvement would be to support non-breaking spaces in FilteringSelect objects.</p>

<p>So you could indent entries in a select-tag.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;addElement(
            'FilteringSelect',
            'comboName',
            array(
                'label'         =&gt; 'description',
                'description'   =&gt; 'description',
                'required'      =&gt; true,
                'value'         =&gt; '',
                'autocomplete'  =&gt; true,
                'multiOptions'  =&gt; array('' =&gt; '', 'test1' =&gt; 'test1', 'test2' =&gt; 'test2'),
                'validators'    =&gt; array('NotEmpty'),
            )
        );  
</code></pre>

<p>Then you could set an option for "multiOptions" param that ```` nothing happens.</p>

<p>I need it if I want display a tree in FilteringSelect objects.</p>

